{"id":573404,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/【立此存照】北京红黄蓝虐童案通报：真评论，假/","date":"2017-11-29T10:58:26Z","modified":"2017-11-29T10:58:26Z","title":"【立此存照】北京红黄蓝虐童案通报：真评论，假评论","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>北京红黄蓝虐童事件的政府官方调查通报发表后，舆论几乎一边倒的质疑声。比如有科技从业人员<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e4%bb%bb%e6%98%93%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%89%e5%8e%9f%e8%89%b2%e5%b9%bc%e5%84%bf%e5%9b%ad%e8%a7%86%e9%a2%91%e7%9b%91%e6%8e%a7%e5%9c%a8%e6%9c%9d%e9%98%b3%e5%8c%ba%e6%95%99%e5%a7%94%e6%9c%89%e6%97%a5%e5%bf%97/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">质疑</a>所谓硬盘损坏后只恢复了113小时监控的<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e5%8f%af%e8%83%bd%e5%90%a7%ef%bd%9c%e7%a1%ac%e7%9b%98%e6%80%bb%e5%9d%8f%ef%bc%8c%e5%9d%8f%e4%ba%ba%e6%80%bb%e9%80%a0%e8%b0%a3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">真实性</a>，而更多的网民则把焦点集中到了<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e6%99%ae%e9%80%9a%e7%be%a4%e4%bc%97-%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e7%90%86%e8%a7%a3%e7%ba%a2%e9%bb%84%e8%93%9d%e4%ba%8b%e4%bb%b6%e7%9a%84%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e9%80%9a%e6%8a%a5/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">漏洞百出的通报本身</a>。北京当局对相关网络评论进行了<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e3%80%90%e7%9c%9f%e7%90%86%e9%83%a8%e3%80%91%e5%b9%b3%e5%ae%89%e6%9c%9d%e9%98%b3%ef%bc%8c%e5%b9%b3%e5%ae%89%e5%8c%97%e4%ba%ac%e8%b4%a6%e5%8f%b7%e6%9c%89%e5%85%b3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">严格管控</a>，数篇引来热传的微信文章很快遭到和谐。<strong>在官方通报微博短时间内收到大量评论后，这些评论内容随即被暂时清空，最后放出来的是一些精心挑选出的大量疑似来自水军的口径一致的亲政府言论。</strong></p>\n<p><strong>据本站不完全统计，截至发稿时，被删除的与红黄蓝虐童案官方通报相关的微信文章包括：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title=\"任易：三原色幼儿园视频监控在朝阳区教委有日志和备份\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e4%bb%bb%e6%98%93%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%89%e5%8e%9f%e8%89%b2%e5%b9%bc%e5%84%bf%e5%9b%ad%e8%a7%86%e9%a2%91%e7%9b%91%e6%8e%a7%e5%9c%a8%e6%9c%9d%e9%98%b3%e5%8c%ba%e6%95%99%e5%a7%94%e6%9c%89%e6%97%a5%e5%bf%97/\">任易：三原色幼儿园视频监控在朝阳区教委有日志和备份</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e5%8f%af%e8%83%bd%e5%90%a7%ef%bd%9c%e7%a1%ac%e7%9b%98%e6%80%bb%e5%9d%8f%ef%bc%8c%e5%9d%8f%e4%ba%ba%e6%80%bb%e9%80%a0%e8%b0%a3/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">可能吧｜阿禅 Jason Ng：硬盘总坏，坏人总造谣</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e6%99%ae%e9%80%9a%e7%be%a4%e4%bc%97-%e5%a6%82%e4%bd%95%e7%90%86%e8%a7%a3%e7%ba%a2%e9%bb%84%e8%93%9d%e4%ba%8b%e4%bb%b6%e7%9a%84%e6%9c%80%e6%96%b0%e9%80%9a%e6%8a%a5/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">普通群众 | 如何理解红黄蓝事件的最新通报</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"少年与白日梦｜一块伟大的硬盘\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e5%b0%91%e5%b9%b4%e4%b8%8e%e7%99%bd%e6%97%a5%e6%a2%a6%ef%bd%9c%e4%b8%80%e5%9d%97%e4%bc%9f%e5%a4%a7%e7%9a%84%e7%a1%ac%e7%9b%98/\">少年与白日梦｜一块伟大的硬盘</a></li>\n</ul>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读</strong>：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%ba%a2%e9%bb%84%e8%93%9d%e5%b9%bc%e5%84%bf%e5%9b%ad%e8%99%90%e7%ab%a5%e6%8c%87%e6%8e%a7%ef%bc%9a%e8%a2%ab%e5%92%8c%e8%b0%90%e7%9a%84%e4%b8%8e/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">【立此存照】红黄蓝幼儿园虐童指控：被和谐的与被稳定的</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Permanent Link to 【真理部】“平安朝阳”有关红黄蓝幼儿园一事的通告\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/11/%e3%80%90%e7%9c%9f%e7%90%86%e9%83%a8%e3%80%91%e5%b9%b3%e5%ae%89%e6%9c%9d%e9%98%b3%ef%bc%8c%e5%b9%b3%e5%ae%89%e5%8c%97%e4%ba%ac%e8%b4%a6%e5%8f%b7%e6%9c%89%e5%85%b3/\" rel=\"bookmark\">【真理部】“平安朝阳”有关红黄蓝幼儿园一事的通告 </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/05/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e8%bf%99%e5%b1%8a%e6%89%a7%e6%b3%95%e8%ae%b0%e5%bd%95%e4%bb%aa%e6%9c%89%e5%85%9a%e6%80%a7%ef%bc%8c%e8%ae%a9%e5%ae%83%e5%9d%8f%e5%b0%b1%e5%9d%8f/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">【网络民议】这届执法记录仪有党性，让它坏就坏</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%e7%ba%a2%e9%bb%84%e8%93%9d%e5%b9%bc%e5%84%bf%e5%9b%ad/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">红黄蓝幼儿园</a>专题</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<h3>网络评论管控举例：</h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_573417\" style=\"width: